    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;Virtual Network Computing (VNC) software provides remote desktop functionality.  This document describes a Uniform Resource Identifier (URI) scheme enabling the launch of VNC clients from other applications.  The scheme specifies parameters useful in securely connecting clients with remote hosts.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
